---
title: Spinach Ravioli with Crispy Salami 3 Easy Steps to a Delicious Dinner
description: A few minutes in a hot pan is all it takes to transform diced salami into the crispy, punchy, and ultra-savory topping of your dreams. You’ll crisp up that salami and sprinkle it over rich, comforting spinach-ricotta ravioli tossed in a creamy garlic sauce with fresh tomato. A side of buttery toasted baguette completes the meal.
